{"tid":1471474,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"美國出晒聲，而家真係應該暫停一下勇武先！","createTime":"2019-08-14T09:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T07:52:27.000Z","uid":52577,"like":96,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"04b972b5d30a8b5907198ed4a7e75816656e455b","tid":1471474,"uid":52577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:32:49.000Z","msg":"先利申，一直都係本土勇武派<br />\n見到而家局勢，UN，trump，同McCarthy都出聲<br />\n覺得勇武先暫停一下先，因為美國一直都講緊peaceful protest。<br />\n我明我地既勇武對比外國真係極小兒科，但要話係完全peaceful又其實真係有d夾硬<br />\n今日好多同路人都幫我地打返個輿論戰，但老實講都只係減少左負面影響。<br />\n岩岩撚狗會都出盡力講尋日單野，我地暫時都唔好再俾子彈對面先，暫時回歸一下和理非，<br />\n睇下美國跟住點做先再部署下一個行動。<br />\n大家真係要冷靜頭腦，唔可以行錯之後既棋而由贏變輸！"},{"pid":"1ac77e3de03d2d92d52bbde1e82331b0305de6c4","tid":1471474,"uid":52577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:43:32.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7887ee694c2ed1c00411ce60e690e2d71e02942f","tid":1471474,"uid":11143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:45:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"081e85669ad9f16598358c0e62ec47d1d94cfe8c","tid":1471474,"uid":52577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:16:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0609a8628cc4da61bf287a97c857231a8bb761ff","tid":1471474,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:41:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03c27133c5c1e74644dbba9d21c4e93aafa19743","tid":1471474,"uid":52577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:25:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e1d6bcd82531e7e4ee26e73baac74510f9fb897","tid":1471474,"uid":52577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:54:28.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"d77aaa66cd14add6d5ebe3c9581ee30dd2b07cca","tid":1471474,"uid":291065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:55:16.000Z","msg":"定格811<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"